data.description: Welcome to your new home in Pentagon City! This cozy 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom condo provides a comfortable and inviting living space that can be customized to suit your personal style. The bedroom has plenty of natural light and includes a spacious closet as well as a walk-in closet for all your storage needs. You can access the private balcony from the bedroom or the living room, providing a peaceful outdoor space to relax in. You'll never have to worry about parking with your own covered, assigned space, ensuring a stress-free arrival home every day. Working at the Pentagon? You’re close enough to walk! The condo is conveniently located walking distance to metro, making commuting easy, and there are plenty of shopping and dining options nearby.  Do you travel often? Regan National Airport is 2.5 mile walk away, or a quick 10 minute drive . This condo offers an incredible opportunity for a dynamic and comfortable lifestyle in the heart of the city, at an incredible price. Don't miss out on the chance to make it your new home!
